      203,
      581,
      287
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "**Câu 1.** Giá trị của $\\lim \\frac{5^n - 1}{3^n + 1}$ bằng :"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      115,
      310,
      212,
      343
    ],
    "category": "List-item",
    "text": "A. $+\\infty$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      470,
      310,
      539,
      343
    ],
    "category": "List-item",
    "text": "B. 1."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      827,
      310,
      884,
      343
    ],
    "category": "List-item",
    "text": "C. 0"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      1175,
      310,
      1272,
      343
    ],
    "category": "List-item",
    "text": "D. $-\\infty$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      727,
      369,
      843,
      406
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Lời giải"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      76,
      426,
      198,
      463
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Chọn A."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      76,
      486,
      550,
      672
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{Ta có: } \\lim \\frac{5^n - 1}{3^n + 1} = \\lim \\frac{1 - \\left(\\frac{1}{5}\\right)^n}{\\left(\\frac{3}{5}\\right)^n + \\left(\\frac{1}{5}\\right)^n}\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      76,
      699,
      1139,
      802
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{Nhưng } \\lim \\left(1 - \\left(\\frac{1}{5}\\right)^n\\right) = 1 > 0, \\lim \\left(\\frac{3}{5}\\right)^n + \\left(\\frac{1}{5}\\right)^n = 0 \\text{ và } \\left(\\frac{3}{5}\\right)^n + \\left(\\frac{1}{5}\\right)^n > 0 \\forall n \\in \\mathbb{N}^*\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      76,
      832,
      359,
      916
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{Nên } \\lim \\frac{5^n - 1}{3^n + 1} = +\\infty.\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
