    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{Mà } x \\in (0; 4\\pi) \\Leftrightarrow 0 < \\frac{\\pi}{4} + k\\pi < 4\\pi \\Leftrightarrow -\\frac{1}{4} < k < \\frac{15}{4}\n$$"
